title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: 2X GTA$ and RP on Nightclub Goods and Doubled Daily Income
content:
Dance floors at Nightclubs citywide are slammed, pulling in 2X GTA$ in Daily Income all week long while the surge lasts.

Pull up your iFruit and call Yohan to Request Nightclub Goods and intercept contraband on incoming cargo shipments and delivery trucks for Double Rewards.

Once you’ve amassed enough product, offload your stash in Nightclub Sell Goods missions, launched from the computers in your Nightclub’s office and warehouse floors, paying out 2X GTA$ and RP through May 1.
